                       "message":  "SCENE-SAVE-SOURCE-PATH: fix stale module doc (post-exec correction)\n\nRound-2 correction (post-exec review). When handle_save_request was reworked\nfor true Save, its function doc was updated but the save_request.rs\nmodule-level # Design header was left saying \"Save-As only (v0)... no\nscene_source_path memory... no silent overwrite yet\" — stale. Rewrite that\nbullet to describe the implemented true-Save-with-Save-As-fallback behavior\n(and the .rge-scene-only tracking), and reword the accurate-but-ambiguous\n\"(Save-As only)\" parenthetical to \"(Save-As path only)\".\n\nAn unbounded stale-prose sweep confirms this was the sole stale reference.\nDoc-only; no runtime logic change.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
